author: The Critical Drinker
description: From flops like Captain America Brave New World and Mickey 17 to action duds like Novocaine, it seems like nothing is working right now. But with theatres pinning their hopes on Rachel Zegler's Snow White, will it get better or worse as we head into the summer movie season?
title: Hollywood's Rough Start To 2025 (And It'll Probably Get Worse)
